#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:1
msgid "Platform API"
msgstr "API de plataforma"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:3
msgid ""
"Platform detection helpers are available under `ptool.platform` and "
"`p.platform`."
msgstr ""
"As utilidades de detecção de plataforma estão disponíveis em `ptool.platform`"
" e `p.platform`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:5
msgid "ptool.platform.os"
msgstr "ptool.platform.os"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.platform.os()` returns the operating system of the current machine."
msgstr "`ptool.platform.os()` retorna o sistema operacional da máquina atual."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:11
msgid "Returns: `linux | macos | windows`."
msgstr "Retorna: `linux | macos | windows`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:17
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:17"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "Comportamento:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:19
msgid "This reports the local machine running `ptool run`."
msgstr "Isso informa a máquina local que está executando `ptool run`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:20
msgid "`ptool` currently exposes `linux`, `macos`, and `windows`."
msgstr "Atualmente, `ptool` expõe `linux`, `macos` e `windows`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:22
msgid "ptool.platform.arch"
msgstr "ptool.platform.arch"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:24
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:24"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:26
msgid ""
"`ptool.platform.arch()` returns the CPU architecture of the current machine."
msgstr "`ptool.platform.arch()` retorna a arquitetura de CPU da máquina atual."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:28
msgid "Returns: `amd64 | arm64 | x86 | arm | riscv64`."
msgstr "Retorna: `amd64 | arm64 | x86 | arm | riscv64`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:34
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:34"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "Comportamento:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:36
msgid "`x86_64` is exposed as `amd64`."
msgstr "`x86_64` é exposto como `amd64`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:37
msgid "`aarch64` is exposed as `arm64`."
msgstr "`aarch64` é exposto como `arm64`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:38
msgid "32-bit x86 variants such as `x86` and `i686` are exposed as `x86`."
msgstr "Variantes x86 de 32 bits, como `x86` e `i686`, são expostas como `x86`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:39
msgid "32-bit ARM variants such as `armv7l` are exposed as `arm`."
msgstr "Variantes ARM de 32 bits, como `armv7l`, são expostas como `arm`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:40
msgid "`riscv64` is exposed as `riscv64`."
msgstr "`riscv64` é exposto como `riscv64`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:42
msgid "ptool.platform.target"
msgstr "ptool.platform.target"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:44
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:44"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:46
msgid ""
"`ptool.platform.target()` returns a normalized platform target string for "
"the current machine."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.platform.target()` retorna uma string de target de plataforma "
"normalizada para a máquina atual."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:49
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "Retorna: `string`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:56
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:56"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "Comportamento:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:58
msgid ""
"The result is always `ptool.platform.os() .. \"-\" .. ptool.platform.arch()`."
msgstr ""
"O resultado é sempre `ptool.platform.os() .. \"-\" .. ptool.platform.arch()`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:59
msgid ""
"This is intended for platform-based branching such as selecting download "
"artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Isso se destina a desvios baseados em plataforma, como selecionar artefatos "
"de download."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/platform.md:61
msgid ""
"Common values include `linux-amd64`, `linux-arm64`, `linux-x86`, `linux-arm`"
", `linux-riscv64`, `macos-amd64`, `macos-arm64`, and `windows-amd64`."
msgstr ""
"Valores comuns incluem `linux-amd64`, `linux-arm64`, `linux-x86`, `linux-arm`"
", `linux-riscv64`, `macos-amd64`, `macos-arm64` e `windows-amd64`."
